#### [NEW] `src/common/` directory
| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `common.module.ts` | Shared module |
| `enums/role.enum.ts` | `ADMIN`, `MANAGER`, `SALESPERSON` |
| `enums/payment-status.enum.ts` | `PENDING`, `PAID`, `CANCELLED` |
| `enums/action-type.enum.ts` | `CREATE`, `UPDATE`, `DELETE`, `LOGIN`, `LOGOUT`, etc. |
| `decorators/roles.decorator.ts` | `@Roles(...)` metadata decorator |
