| `guards/roles.guard.ts` | RBAC roles guard |
| `filters/http-exception.filter.ts` | Global exception filter (sanitizes errors in production) |
| `interceptors/logging.interceptor.ts` | Request/response logging |
| `dto/pagination.dto.ts` | Shared pagination query DTO |
| `dto/api-response.dto.ts` | Standardized response wrapper |

