#### [NEW] `src/users/` directory
| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `users.module.ts` | Module |
| `users.controller.ts` | CRUD: `GET /users`, `GET /users/:id`, `POST /users`, `PATCH /users/:id`, `DELETE /users/:id`, `POST /users/:id/reset-password`, `POST /users/:id/force-logout` |
| `users.service.ts` | Business logic, password hashing, deactivation |
| `dto/create-user.dto.ts` | Validated DTO |
| `dto/update-user.dto.ts` | Partial update DTO |
| `dto/reset-password.dto.ts` | New password DTO |

**Edge cases:** cannot deactivate yourself, cannot change own role, strong password policy.

