### Phase 7 — Warehouse & Stock Module

#### [NEW] `src/warehouses/` directory
| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `warehouses.module.ts` | Module |
| `warehouses.controller.ts` | CRUD: `GET`, `POST`, `PATCH`, `DELETE` |
| `warehouses.service.ts` | Business logic |
| `dto/create-warehouse.dto.ts` | DTO |
| `dto/update-warehouse.dto.ts` | DTO |

#### [NEW] `src/stock/` directory
| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `stock.module.ts` | Module |
| `stock.controller.ts` | `GET /stock`, `POST /stock/add`, `POST /stock/assign`, `GET /stock/assignments` |
| `stock.service.ts` | Add stock to warehouse, assign stock to salesperson, prevent negative stock (pessimistic locking) |
| `dto/add-stock.dto.ts` | DTO |
| `dto/assign-stock.dto.ts` | DTO |

**Anti-tampering:** `SELECT ... FOR UPDATE` lock on stock rows during assignment.

---

### Phase 8 — Sales Module

#### [NEW] `src/sales/` directory
| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `sales.module.ts` | Module |
| `sales.controller.ts` | `POST /sales`, `GET /sales`, `GET /sales/:id`, `POST /sales/:id/cancel` |
| `sales.service.ts` | **Full transaction**: BEGIN → lock assignment → validate qty → insert sale → insert items → deduct remaining → log activity → COMMIT |
| `dto/create-sale.dto.ts` | items array, idempotency_key (header) |
| `dto/sale-item.dto.ts` | product_id, quantity |

**Edge cases:**
- Idempotency key to prevent double submission
- Pessimistic locking to prevent concurrent overselling
- Only ADMIN can cancel a sale
- Cancelled sale restores stock to assignment

---

### Phase 9 — Activity Log Module

#### [NEW] `src/activity-log/` directory
| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `activity-log.module.ts` | Global module |
| `activity-log.service.ts` | Insert-only log service, SHA-256 hash chain (`current_hash = SHA256(previous_hash + JSON.stringify(record))`) |
| `activity-log.controller.ts` | `GET /activity-logs` (paginated, filtered), `GET /activity-logs/verify` (chain integrity check) |
| `activity-log.interceptor.ts` | Auto-logs mutations (POST/PATCH/DELETE) with old + new data |

**Anti-tampering:** No UPDATE/DELETE on activity_logs table. Database-level rule + app-level guard. Hash chain verification endpoint.

---

### Phase 10 — Dashboard Module

#### [NEW] `src/dashboard/` directory
| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `dashboard.module.ts` | Module |
| `dashboard.controller.ts` | `GET /dashboard/admin`, `GET /dashboard/salesperson` |
